## Hardware

### Microcontroller
- STM32 (F4 series)
- USB CDC serial @115200 baud

### Sensors
| Sensor | Bus | Purpose |
|--------|-----|---------|
| MMC5603 S1 | I2C1 | Ball tracking |
| MMC5603 S2 | I2C2 | Ball tracking |
| MMC5603 S3 | I2C3 | Compass (far from ball, reads Earth field) |
| MPU6050 | I2C2 (shared with S2) | Accelerometer + Gyroscope |

### Serial Format (12 values @115200)
```
ax, ay, az,         ← MPU6050 accel (raw/16384 → g)
m1x, m1y, m1z,     ← S1 magnetometer raw counts
m2x, m2y, m2z,     ← S2 magnetometer raw counts
cx, cy, cz          ← S3 compass raw counts
```

